<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/2277?language=en' lang='en'>
Do we see reality as it is? 
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
