<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1227391' id='t-1227391'>and they do show that our perceptions
have been shaped</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1229969' id='t-1229969'>not to show us reality as it is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1231849' id='t-1231849'>but that does not mean the same thing
