</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
21:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1263613' id='t-1263613'>CA: I mean, really what you're proposing
