<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1267607' id='t-1267607'>interpretation of the world:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1269998' id='t-1269998'>consciousness causes matter,
not the other way around.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
21:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1272947' id='t-1272947'>DH: Well, it's slightly
