</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
21:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1291235' id='t-1291235'>CA: Don, I could literally talk with you
